If you are a txt2tags user upgrading from a previous 1.x version,
please read the "Upgrade Guide"[1], as major changes were made
on the program and the compatibility was broken. Your existing
.t2t files may not work!

   [1] Upgrade Guide - http://txt2tags.sf.net/v2-upgrade.html

